                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Check local listings for specific times.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="md:col-span-2 border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-4 py-2">
                    <p class="text-lg nsw-detail-label mb-1">Location</p>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 font-medium">Municipal Auditorium (or address placeholder)</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Public access: Yes | Parking: Limited</p>
